<TEXT>
<P>
Awarding reparations to descendants of slaves makes about as much sense as 
awarding reparations to the descendants of 360,000 Union soldiers who died 
fighting a war that freed the slaves; even less. 
</P>
<P>
JAMES GALLAGHER 
</P>
<P>
Santa Monica 
