<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH SURELOCK; 
</P>
<P>
THE SILICON SLEUTH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SURELOCK's wagers for today are a $2 daily double wheel, Movinandimprovin in 
the first race to the field in the second race, a $50 exacta, Wedding Bouquet 
to Somethingmerry, and a $20 exacta reversing the two in the eighth race. 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $1,158 
</P>
<P>
Bob Mieszerski's bet is a $30 win parlay, Jazzy Me in the fifth race to Craig 
Ronald in the seventh. 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $1,542.20 
</P>
<P>
Both started with $2,000 bankrolls. 
</P>
