couple met at a Single Sailors Club in Long Beach. ; Photo, Gene Carapetyan and 
Louanne Peck sail My Sweet Lord at finish of Honolulu-to-Hiroshima race. It was 
sixth among 10 in its class. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
