<HEADLINE>
<P>
AZTECS GIVE COACH CONTRACT EXTENSION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
San Diego State football Coach Al Luginbill received a one-year contract 
extension to lead the Aztecs through the 1993 season, Athletic Director Fred 
Miller announced. 
</P>
<P>
Luginbill directed San Diego State to back-to-back winning seasons for the 
first time since 1981-82. The Aztecs were 6-5 this season. 
</P>
